lead_paragraph: Hundreds of unionized workers lashed out at Carl Icahn on Friday, picketing the Trump Taj Mahal Casino where the billionaire activist seeks to terminate health-care and pension plans.

headline.main: Atlantic City Trump Casino Workers Picket, Target Investor Icahn
